item.description: Java - A quick introduction Java is one of the widely used application development language across many domains. James Gosling created the language during the year 1995 and since then it has matured every release. There are thousands of developers who work on this programming language and have built their carrier. Even after two decades of development the language still has demand in the market and has attracted a lot of young developers.
